From: Christoph Hellwig <hch@lst.de>
Date: Wed, 11 Mar 2026 08:03:58 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] random: factor out a __limit_random_u32_below helper

Factor out the guts of __get_random_u32_below into a new helper, so that
callers with their own prng state can reuse this code.

Link: https://lkml.kernel.org/r/20260311070416.972667-27-hch@lst.de
